author: nataliaratnikova
body:
Hi Lina, 

please take for the HG1711 cmsweb release. 

This PR includes changes from earlier PR #3515 for  the reserved queue, plus fixes for the SL7 build. 
I also merged all other developments from the comp_gcc630  branch, so hopefully you do not need to cherry-pick.  

I tested that PHEDEX_combined-web and  whole comp build on vocms055 from this branch.
I did not touch  comp_gcc493 branch, because SLC6 build was successful. 

Please let me know when new phedex web can be tested/validated on cmsweb testbed.  
Thanks a lot,
  Natalia.
